thread.title: Union accepts proposed labor deal at Alcoa Intalco aluminum smelter
thread.title_full: Union accepts proposed labor deal at Alcoa Intalco aluminum smelter | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: Union accepts proposed labor deal at Alcoa Intalco aluminum smelter
text:
Oct 16 Workers at Alcoa's Intalco Works aluminum smelter voted to accept the company's final contract offer, staving off a second labor dispute at a U.S. smelter this year as prices tumble below production costs.
"The Contract was accepted," The international Association of Machinists & Aerospace Workers said on its website. (Reporting by Melanie Burton; Editing by Richard Pullin )
